This project is simulate Buffon needles problem .

Buffon_needle.m is main . It define the GUI and some default values .

sermap.m is to get some value and draw the game place .

needles.m is to simulate drop needles .

rrr.m is which probability to drop needles .


Usage:
win:
if you don't have MATLAB you can find MCRInstaller.exe and install it ,
then you can run Buffon_needle.exe .
else
you can open Buffon_needle.m and use MATLABto run it .

